Description: Advanced WiFi security auditing and penetration testing tool
 WiFi-Nightmare is an advanced WiFi security auditing and penetration
 testing tool. It combines a Python CLI with optional ESP32/ESP8266
 firmware for Evil Twin, Deauthentication, Handshake capture, WPS
 Pixie Dust, and captive portal attacks.
 .
 Features include network scanning with MAC vendor lookup,
 deauthentication attacks, WPA/WPA2 handshake capture, SSID reveal,
 Evil Twin attacks (ESP or software-only), WPS Pixie Dust attacks,
 a multi-OEM captive portal system, and persistent database storage.
